<p>I used for internationalization the JSF configuration, and I have a list of countries from the class <code>Locale</code> in <code>&lt;p:selectOneMenu&gt;</code>, but I am facing a problem of duplicate values of the countries list in <code>&lt;p:selectOneMenu&gt;</code> when I change the language of the page </p>  <p>How can I correct this problem?</p>  <pre><code>private List&lt;String&gt; countriesList = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();      public void setCountriesList(List&lt;String&gt; countriesList) {         this.countriesList = countriesList;     }      public List&lt;String&gt; getCountriesList() {          String[] locales = Locale.getISOCountries();          for (String countryCode : locales) {              Locale obj = new Locale("", countryCode);             countriesList.add(obj.getDisplayCountry(Locale.ENGLISH));          }         Collections.sort(countriesList);         return countriesList;     } </code></pre>